title: Bike Carrier Rear - Thule Clip On High
description:
Watch this step by step instruction video and learn how easy it is to install the Thule ClipOn High rear bike rack by yourself. 

Thule ClipOn High 9105, 9106
The fast mounting and foldable bike carrier designed for station wagons and hatchbacks (for 2 bikes).

- The raised position of the carrier keeps the rear lights and number plate visible.
- All parts in contact with the car and bikes are coated with rubber for extra protection.
- All bike frame holders are detachable for convenient mounting of bikes.
- Easy to mount to the rear door with a unique snap-on system.
- Quick-release straps, adjustable for different wheel sizes.
- Extendable wheel trays for large bikes.
- Quickly folds for easy storage.
- Outer bike position lockable to carrier.
- This product does not have universal fit. The ClipOn High carrier comes in two versions (9105 and 9106) having different tube diameters fitting different car models. Please visit Thule.com for information related to specific car models.

Learn more at www.thule.com
